spec_data.Name: kf5-libkdcraw
spec_data.Description:
Libkdcraw is a C++ interface around LibRaw library used to decode RAW
picture files. More information about LibRaw can be found at
http://www.libraw.org.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Mon 02 Oct 2017 04:54:44 PM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: A C++ interface around LibRaw library
